 《摇滚学校》原声带首次登陆流媒体https://www.nme.com/news/music/school-of-rock-soundtrack-arrives-on-streaming-for-the-first-time-3763843?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=school-of-rock-原声带首次登陆流媒体Emma WilkesSat, 08 Jun 2024 11:41:38 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3763843 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="摇滚学院" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>其中包括一首新曲目“In The End Of Time”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/school-of-rock-soundtrack-arrives-on-streaming-for-the-first-time-3763843">《School Of Rock》原声带首次登陆流媒体，并</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="摇滚学院" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-black">杰克·布莱克</a>2003 年音乐喜剧<em>《摇滚学校》</em>的原声带首次登陆流媒体服务。</p><p>原版<em>《School of Rock》</em> <em>（音乐源自电影并受电影启发）</em>专辑收录了演员们演唱的歌曲，包括主打歌和翻唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/acdc">AC/DC</a>的《It&#39;s a Long Way to the Top》（如果你想摇滚） n&#39; Roll)&#39; 以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-who">The Who</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-doors">The Doors</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-nicks">Stevie Nicks、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">Led Zeppelin</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ramones">Ramones</a>等乐队的热门歌曲。它还包括一首新歌“In The End Of Time”</p><p>在这部电影中，布莱克饰演杜威·芬恩，一位苦苦挣扎的音乐家，他冒充代课老师“施尼布利先生”，以赚更多的钱并向班级教授摇滚乐。这部电影取得了巨大成功，预算为 3500 万美元，全球票房收入为 1.31 亿美元，后来被改编成音乐剧和尼克频道系列剧，于 2016 年至 2018 年播出三季。</p><p>去年，这部电影庆祝了上映 20 周年，布莱克为此<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jack-black-confirms-school-of-rock-20th-anniversary-reunion-3426356">组织了一次演员聚会。</a>他还表示，只要原电影的编剧迈克·怀特参与其中，他就<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jack-black-ready-school-of-rock-3607581">愿意制作续集</a>。怀特在影片中饰演杜威的室友内德·施内卜利 (Ned Schneebly)，他因创作、编剧和导演 HBO 热门剧集<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/the-white-lotus-review-3017677"><em>《白莲花》</em></a>而闻名。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7665EvJPat/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 